"1" = "I must endure the presence@of a few caterpillars@if I wish to become acquainted@with the butterflies";
"2" = "The most beautiful things in the world@cannot be seen or touched,@they are felt with the heart";
"3" = "It is the time you have wasted@for your rose@that makes your rose so important";
"4" = "No one is ever satisfied where he is";
"5" = "If you love a flower that lives on a star,@it is sweet to look at the sky at night.@All the stars are a-bloom with flowers";
"6" = "It is such a mysterious place,@the land of tears";
"7" = "What makes the desert beautiful@is that somewhere it hides a well";

"8" = "I am who I am@and@I have the need to be";
"9" = "To forget a friend is sad.@Not everyone has had a friend";
"10" = "And so it will be@as if all the stars were laughing,@when you look at the sky at night";
"11" = "And when your sorrow is comforted@(time soothes all sorrows)@you will be content@that you have known me";

"12" = "I remembered the fox.@One runs the risk of crying a bit@if one allows oneself to be tamed";
"13" = "The only things you learn@are the things you tame";
"14" = "You become responsible,@forever,@for what you have tamed";
"15" = "You see, one loves the sunset@when one is so sad";
"16" = "It is much more difficult@to judge oneself@than to judge others";
"17" = "What matters most@are the simple pleasures@so abundant that@we can all enjoy them";

"18" = "It is only with the heart@that one can see rightly";
"19" ="what is essential@is invisible to the eye";
"20" = "Words are the source@of misunderstandings";
"21" = "All grown-ups were once children@but only few of them remember it";
"22" = "The thing that is important@is the thing that is not seen";
"23" = "I wonder whether the stars@are set alight in heaven@so that one day each one of us@may find his own again";
"24" = "Only the children@know what they are looking for";

